    "en": {
      "title": "Seven hours of water cut today in Colombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Water Supply and Drainage Board has informed that the water supply will be suspended for seven hours today to carry out corrections for the development of the water supply network.",
        "Water supply will be suspended from 11.00 pm today (23) to 6.00 am tomorrow.",
        "Accordingly, the National Water Supply and Drainage Board has announced that supply will be suspended at Colombo 7, 8, 9 and 10. (a)"
      ],
